sentences.content: I told [my stroke story](mystrokevc,page) during the Virtual Connections Member Spotlight.
I sent out a email beforehand to remind my friends to come and support me.
Over seventy people joined to listen to me speak!
Many of my friends with aphasia attended to support me.
I spoke for over twenty minutes.
The audience congratulated me when I was done.
They asked me a lot of questions.
I thanked Katie, Emily and Bri for helping me.
This was the final Spotlight of the semester.
We attended Sunil and Anisha's Mehndi party at Aruna's home.
I wore my sari from Aruna's bridal party over 30 years ago.
Wen did his best to iron and wrap the sari around me.
They served indian food and wood fired pizza.
